\fISuggestedSessionId\fR is a \fIbinary()\fR, \fIPeerCert\fR is a DER-encoded certificate, \fICompression\fR is an enumeration integer, and \fICipherSuite\fR is of type \fIerl_cipher_suite()\fR.


