\fB          gen_tcp:listen_option() |\fR
\fB          gen_udp:option().\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Options for the transport socket.

.PP
The default socket options are \fI[{mode, list}, {packet, 0}, {header, 0}, {active, true}]\fR.

.PP
For valid options, see \fIinet\fR, \fIgen_tcp\fR, and \fIgen_udp\fR in Kernel. Note that stream-oriented options such as \fIpacket\fR are only relevant for TLS and not DTLS.


