.B
\fBeccs(Version) -> NamedCurves\fR
\fB              when\fR
\fB                  Version ::\fR
\fB                      'tlsv1.2' | 'tlsv1.1' | tlsv1 | 'dtlsv1.2' |\fR
\fB                      dtlsv1,\fR
\fB                  NamedCurves :: [named_curve()].\fR

.br
.RS
.PP
Returns the elliptic curves supported by default for \fIVersion\fR.

