The \fIConsumeSecret\fR argument is relevant only in TLS-1.3, causing the TLS-1.3 \fIexporter_master_secret\fR to be consumed, thereby making it unavailable and increasing security. Further attempts to call this function will fail.


.RE
.B
\fBfilter_cipher_suites(Suites, Filters) -> Ciphers\fR
\fB                              when\fR
\fB                                  Suites :: ciphers(),\fR
